---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-black/10 mt-16 bg-white/50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[960px] px-4 md:px-8 py-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3 text-sm">
    <div>
      <div class="font-mono text-[0.82rem] font-medium tracking-[0.03em] text-ink">AI<span class="text-[#c94f1e]">SecOps</span></div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[#6b6460] leading-relaxed">Security for agentic AI systems at runtime: policy enforcement, containment, and auditable execution.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[#6b6460]">Resources</div>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[#6b6460]">
        <li><a href="/definition" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">Definition</a></li>
        <li><a href="/threat-model" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">Threat Model</a></li>
        <li><a href="/reference-architecture" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">Reference Architecture</a></li>
        <li><a href="/open-source" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">Open Source</a></li>
        <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="no-underline hover:text-ink">RSS</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[#6b6460]">Get updates</div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[#6b6460]">Get the whitepaper + new posts.</p>

      <form name="aisecops-updates" method="POST" data-netlify="true" action="/thank-you" class="mt-4 space-y-2">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="aisecops-updates" />
        <input name="email" type="email" required placeholder="you@company.com"
          class="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-md bg-white border border-black/15 text-ink placeholder:text-[#8a837f] focus:outline-none focus:border-[#c94f1e]" />
        <button type="submit"
          class="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-[3px] bg-[#c94f1e] hover:bg-[#a83d12] border border-[#c94f1e] text-white font-mono text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.04em] uppercase">
          Notify me
        </button>
        <div class="text-xs text-[#8a837f]">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</div>
      </form>

      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="mailto:hello@aisecops.net" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-[3px] border border-black/15 bg-white text-ink no-underline hover:border-black/30">Email</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/viplavfauzdar/aisecops-lab" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-[3px] border border-black/15 bg-white text-ink no-underline hover:border-black/30">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center text-xs text-[#8a837f] pb-8">© {year} AISecOps. All rights reserved.</div>
</footer>
